{
  "video_id": "iE7YRHxwoDs",
  "title": "Shimon Schocken: The self-organizing computer course",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 18906.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18906.0,
      "end_time": 21872.0,
      "text": "So, this is my grandfather,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21872.0,
      "end_time": 23373.0,
      "text": "Salman Schocken,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23373.0,
      "end_time": 27810.0,
      "text": "who was born into a poor and uneducated family"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27810.0,
      "end_time": 31247.0,
      "text": "with six children to feed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31247.0,
      "end_time": 34943.0,
      "text": "and when he was 14 years old, he was forced to"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34943.0,
      "end_time": 38903.0,
      "text": "drop out of school in order to help put bread on the table."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38903.0,
      "end_time": 42323.0,
      "text": "He never went back to school."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42323.0,
      "end_time": 46470.0,
      "text": "Instead, he went on to build a glittering empire"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 46470.0,
      "end_time": 48578.0,
      "text": "of department stores."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48578.0,
      "end_time": 51831.0,
      "text": "Salman was the consummate perfectionist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51831.0,
      "end_time": 54395.0,
      "text": "and every one of his stores was a jewel"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54395.0,
      "end_time": 56324.0,
      "text": "of Bauhaus architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56324.0,
      "end_time": 59514.0,
      "text": "He was also the ultimate self-learner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59514.0,
      "end_time": 62417.0,
      "text": "and like everything else, he did it in grand style."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62417.0,
      "end_time": 65105.0,
      "text": "He surrounded himself with an entourage"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65105.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68492.0,
      "text": "of young, unknown scholars like Martin Buber"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68492.0,
      "end_time": 71631.0,
      "text": "and Shai Agnon and Franz Kafka,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71631.0,
      "end_time": 74556.0,
      "text": "and he paid each one of them a monthly salary"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74556.0,
      "end_time": 77607.0,
      "text": "so that they could write in peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77607.0,
      "end_time": 82544.0,
      "text": "And yet, in the late &#39;30s, Salman saw what&#39;s coming."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82544.0,
      "end_time": 85858.0,
      "text": "He fled Germany, together with his family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85858.0,
      "end_time": 87947.0,
      "text": "leaving everything else behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 87947.0,
      "end_time": 91157.0,
      "text": "His department stores confiscated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 91157.0,
      "end_time": 94246.0,
      "text": "he spent the rest of his life in a relentless pursuit"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94246.0,
      "end_time": 96715.0,
      "text": "of art and culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96715.0,
      "end_time": 98654.0,
      "text": "This high school dropout"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 98654.0,
      "end_time": 100934.0,
      "text": "died at the age of 82,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100934.0,
      "end_time": 105063.0,
      "text": "a formidable intellectual, cofounder and first CEO"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 105063.0,
      "end_time": 107208.0,
      "text": "of the Hebrew University of Jerusalem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107208.0,
      "end_time": 108972.0,
      "text": "and founder of Schocken Books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108972.0,
      "end_time": 112343.0,
      "text": "an acclaimed imprint that was later acquired"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 112343.0,
      "end_time": 114013.0,
      "text": "by Random House."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114013.0,
      "end_time": 117989.0,
      "text": "Such is the power of self-study."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117989.0,
      "end_time": 120505.0,
      "text": "And these are my parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120505.0,
      "end_time": 124552.0,
      "text": "They too did not enjoy the privilege of college education."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124552.0,
      "end_time": 128523.0,
      "text": "They were too busy building a family and a country."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128523.0,
      "end_time": 132551.0,
      "text": "And yet, just like Salman, they were lifelong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132551.0,
      "end_time": 136309.0,
      "text": "tenacious self-learners, and our home was stacked"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 136309.0,
      "end_time": 140472.0,
      "text": "with thousands of books, records and artwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 140472.0,
      "end_time": 142868.0,
      "text": "I remember quite vividly my father telling me"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142868.0,
      "end_time": 147700.0,
      "text": "that when everyone in the neighborhood will have a TV set,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 147700.0,
      "end_time": 152318.0,
      "text": "then we&#39;ll buy a normal F.M. radio. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 152318.0,
      "end_time": 155347.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 155347.0,
      "end_time": 157071.0,
      "text": "I was going to say holding my first abacus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 157071.0,
      "end_time": 160082.0,
      "text": "but actually holding what my father would consider"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 160082.0,
      "end_time": 163034.0,
      "text": "an ample substitute to an iPad. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 163034.0,
      "end_time": 166696.0,
      "text": "So one thing that I took from home is this notion"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 166696.0,
      "end_time": 169537.0,
      "text": "that educators don&#39;t necessarily have to teach."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 169537.0,
      "end_time": 172766.0,
      "text": "Instead, they can provide an environment and resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 172766.0,
      "end_time": 177914.0,
      "text": "that tease out your natural ability to learn on your own."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 177914.0,
      "end_time": 182008.0,
      "text": "Self-study, self-exploration, self-empowerment:"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 182008.0,
      "end_time": 185328.0,
      "text": "these are the virtues of a great education."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 185328.0,
      "end_time": 189523.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;d like to share with you a story about a self-study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 189523.0,
      "end_time": 192077.0,
      "text": "self-empowering computer science course"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 192077.0,
      "end_time": 196263.0,
      "text": "that I built, together with my brilliant colleague Noam Nisan."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 196263.0,
      "end_time": 199020.0,
      "text": "As you can see from the pictures, both Noam and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 199020.0,
      "end_time": 202438.0,
      "text": "had an early fascination with first principles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 202438.0,
      "end_time": 203960.0,
      "text": "and over the years, as our knowledge of"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 203960.0,
      "end_time": 207535.0,
      "text": "science and technology became more sophisticated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 207535.0,
      "end_time": 210731.0,
      "text": "this early awe with the basics"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 210731.0,
      "end_time": 212831.0,
      "text": "has only intensified."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 212831.0,
      "end_time": 216530.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s not surprising that, about 12 years ago, when"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216530.0,
      "end_time": 220012.0,
      "text": "Noam and I were already computer science professors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 220012.0,
      "end_time": 223764.0,
      "text": "we were equally frustrated by the same phenomenon."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 223764.0,
      "end_time": 226582.0,
      "text": "As computers became increasingly more complex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226582.0,
      "end_time": 229786.0,
      "text": "our students were losing the forest for the trees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 229786.0,
      "end_time": 232873.0,
      "text": "and indeed, it is impossible to connect"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 232873.0,
      "end_time": 235515.0,
      "text": "with the soul of the machine if you interact"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 235515.0,
      "end_time": 238924.0,
      "text": "with a black box P.C. or a Mac which is shrouded"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 238924.0,
      "end_time": 242300.0,
      "text": "by numerous layers of closed, proprietary software."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 242300.0,
      "end_time": 245990.0,
      "text": "So Noam and I had this insight that if we want our students"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 245990.0,
      "end_time": 248009.0,
      "text": "to understand how computers work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 248009.0,
      "end_time": 251097.0,
      "text": "and understand it in the marrow of their bones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 251097.0,
      "end_time": 252658.0,
      "text": "then perhaps the best way to go about it"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 252658.0,
      "end_time": 257252.0,
      "text": "is to have them build a complete, working,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 257252.0,
      "end_time": 260964.0,
      "text": "general-purpose, useful computer, hardware and software,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 260964.0,
      "end_time": 264494.0,
      "text": "from the ground up, from first principles."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 264494.0,
      "end_time": 268702.0,
      "text": "Now, we had to start somewhere, and so Noam and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 268702.0,
      "end_time": 272192.0,
      "text": "decided to base our cathedral, so to speak,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 272192.0,
      "end_time": 275331.0,
      "text": "on the simplest possible building block,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 275331.0,
      "end_time": 278132.0,
      "text": "which is something called NAND."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 278132.0,
      "end_time": 282070.0,
      "text": "It is nothing more than a trivial logic gate"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 282070.0,
      "end_time": 285108.0,
      "text": "with four input-output states."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 285108.0,
      "end_time": 287774.0,
      "text": "So we now start this journey by telling our students"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 287774.0,
      "end_time": 289842.0,
      "text": "that God gave us NAND — (Laughter) —"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 289842.0,
      "end_time": 293827.0,
      "text": "and told us to build a computer, and when we asked how,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 293827.0,
      "end_time": 297011.0,
      "text": "God said, &quot;One step at a time.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 297011.0,
      "end_time": 300104.0,
      "text": "And then, following this advice, we start"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 300104.0,
      "end_time": 303063.0,
      "text": "with this lowly, humble NAND gate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 303063.0,
      "end_time": 305003.0,
      "text": "and we walk our students through an elaborate sequence"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 305003.0,
      "end_time": 308740.0,
      "text": "of projects in which they gradually build a chip set,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 308740.0,
      "end_time": 312852.0,
      "text": "a hardware platform, an assembler, a virtual machine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 312852.0,
      "end_time": 316429.0,
      "text": "a basic operating system and a compiler"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 316429.0,
      "end_time": 322618.0,
      "text": "for a simple, Java-like language that we call &quot;JACK.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 322618.0,
      "end_time": 325166.0,
      "text": "The students celebrate the end of this tour de force"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 325166.0,
      "end_time": 328000.0,
      "text": "by using JACK to write all sorts of cool games"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 328000.0,
      "end_time": 330992.0,
      "text": "like Pong, Snake and Tetris."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 330992.0,
      "end_time": 334607.0,
      "text": "You can imagine the tremendous joy of playing"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 334607.0,
      "end_time": 337631.0,
      "text": "with a Tetris game that you wrote in JACK"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 337631.0,
      "end_time": 340421.0,
      "text": "and then compiled into machine language in a compiler"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 340421.0,
      "end_time": 342829.0,
      "text": "that you wrote also, and then seeing the result"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 342829.0,
      "end_time": 345712.0,
      "text": "running on a machine that you built starting"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 345712.0,
      "end_time": 348996.0,
      "text": "with nothing more than a few thousand NAND gates."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 348996.0,
      "end_time": 352186.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a tremendous personal triumph of going"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 352186.0,
      "end_time": 356911.0,
      "text": "from first principles all the way to a fantastically complex"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 356911.0,
      "end_time": 359262.0,
      "text": "and useful system."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 359262.0,
      "end_time": 363659.0,
      "text": "Noam and I worked five years to facilitate"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 363659.0,
      "end_time": 366867.0,
      "text": "this ascent and to create the tools and infrastructure"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 366867.0,
      "end_time": 370040.0,
      "text": "that will enable students to build it in one semester."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 370040.0,
      "end_time": 374079.0,
      "text": "And this is the great team that helped us make it happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 374079.0,
      "end_time": 378326.0,
      "text": "The trick was to decompose the computer&#39;s construction"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 378326.0,
      "end_time": 381280.0,
      "text": "into numerous stand-alone modules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 381280.0,
      "end_time": 385180.0,
      "text": "each of which could be individually specified,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 385180.0,
      "end_time": 390415.0,
      "text": "built and unit-tested in isolation from the rest of the project."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 390415.0,
      "end_time": 393404.0,
      "text": "And from day one, Noam and I decided to put"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 393404.0,
      "end_time": 396940.0,
      "text": "all these building blocks freely available in open source"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 396940.0,
      "end_time": 398420.0,
      "text": "on the Web."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 398420.0,
      "end_time": 402891.0,
      "text": "So chip specifications, APIs, project descriptions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 402891.0,
      "end_time": 406795.0,
      "text": "software tools, hardware simulators, CPU emulators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 406795.0,
      "end_time": 410497.0,
      "text": "stacks of hundreds of slides, lectures --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 410497.0,
      "end_time": 412724.0,
      "text": "we laid out everything on the Web"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 412724.0,
      "end_time": 415751.0,
      "text": "and invited the world to come over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 415751.0,
      "end_time": 417287.0,
      "text": "take whatever they need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 417287.0,
      "end_time": 419677.0,
      "text": "and do whatever they want with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 419677.0,
      "end_time": 423576.0,
      "text": "And then something fascinating happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 423576.0,
      "end_time": 425159.0,
      "text": "The world came."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 425159.0,
      "end_time": 428317.0,
      "text": "And in short order, thousands of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 428317.0,
      "end_time": 429861.0,
      "text": "were building our machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 429861.0,
      "end_time": 433785.0,
      "text": "And NAND2Tetris became one of the first"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 433785.0,
      "end_time": 437015.0,
      "text": "massive, open, online courses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 437015.0,
      "end_time": 439759.0,
      "text": "although seven years ago we had no idea that what"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 439759.0,
      "end_time": 441920.0,
      "text": "we were doing is called MOOCs."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 441920.0,
      "end_time": 445778.0,
      "text": "We just observed how self-organized courses"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 445778.0,
      "end_time": 448860.0,
      "text": "were kind of spontaneously spawning"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 448860.0,
      "end_time": 450243.0,
      "text": "out of our materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 450243.0,
      "end_time": 453334.0,
      "text": "For example, Pramode C.E.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 453334.0,
      "end_time": 455243.0,
      "text": "an engineer from Kerala, India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 455243.0,
      "end_time": 457052.0,
      "text": "has organized groups of self-learners"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 457052.0,
      "end_time": 460096.0,
      "text": "who build our computer under his good guidance."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 460096.0,
      "end_time": 463118.0,
      "text": "And Parag Shah, another engineer, from Mumbai,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 463118.0,
      "end_time": 465963.0,
      "text": "has unbundled our projects into smaller,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 465963.0,
      "end_time": 467985.0,
      "text": "more manageable bites that he now serves"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 467985.0,
      "end_time": 471787.0,
      "text": "in his pioneering do-it-yourself computer science program."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 471787.0,
      "end_time": 475198.0,
      "text": "The people who are attracted to these courses"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 475198.0,
      "end_time": 477618.0,
      "text": "typically have a hacker mentality."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 477618.0,
      "end_time": 479723.0,
      "text": "They want to figure out how things work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 479723.0,
      "end_time": 481483.0,
      "text": "and they want to do it in groups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 481483.0,
      "end_time": 484294.0,
      "text": "like this hackers club in Washington, D.C.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 484294.0,
      "end_time": 487959.0,
      "text": "that uses our materials to offer community courses."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 487959.0,
      "end_time": 490905.0,
      "text": "And because these materials are widely available"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 490905.0,
      "end_time": 493599.0,
      "text": "and open-source, different people take them"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 493599.0,
      "end_time": 496542.0,
      "text": "to very different and unpredictable directions."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 496542.0,
      "end_time": 499455.0,
      "text": "For example, Yu Fangmin, from Guangzhou,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 499455.0,
      "end_time": 502301.0,
      "text": "has used FPGA technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 502301.0,
      "end_time": 506026.0,
      "text": "to build our computer and show others how to do the same"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 506026.0,
      "end_time": 509389.0,
      "text": "using a video clip, and Ben Craddock developed"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 509389.0,
      "end_time": 512990.0,
      "text": "a very nice computer game that unfolds"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 512990.0,
      "end_time": 517959.0,
      "text": "inside our CPU architecture, which is quite a complex"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 517958.99999999994,
      "end_time": 520443.99999999994,
      "text": "3D maze that Ben developed"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 520443.99999999994,
      "end_time": 524352.0,
      "text": "using the Minecraft 3D simulator engine."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 524352.0,
      "end_time": 527370.0,
      "text": "The Minecraft community went bananas over this project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 527370.0,
      "end_time": 530754.0,
      "text": "and Ben became an instant media celebrity."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 530754.0,
      "end_time": 533656.0,
      "text": "And indeed, for quite a few people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 533656.0,
      "end_time": 537733.0,
      "text": "taking this NAND2Tetris pilgrimage, if you will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 537733.0,
      "end_time": 540445.0,
      "text": "has turned into a life-changing experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 540445.0,
      "end_time": 543634.0,
      "text": "For example, take Dan Rounds, who is a music"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 543634.0,
      "end_time": 546403.0,
      "text": "and math major from East Lansing, Michigan."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 546403.0,
      "end_time": 549847.0,
      "text": "A few weeks ago, Dan posted a victorious post"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 549847.0,
      "end_time": 552467.0,
      "text": "on our website, and I&#39;d like to read it to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 552467.0,
      "end_time": 555925.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s what Dan said."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 555925.0,
      "end_time": 558737.0,
      "text": "&quot;I did the coursework because understanding computers"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 558737.0,
      "end_time": 562083.0,
      "text": "is important to me, just like literacy and numeracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 562083.0,
      "end_time": 565100.0,
      "text": "and I made it through. I never worked harder on anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 565100.0,
      "end_time": 567809.0,
      "text": "never been challenged to this degree."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 567809.0,
      "end_time": 570196.0,
      "text": "But given what I now feel capable of doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 570196.0,
      "end_time": 572354.0,
      "text": "I would certainly do it again."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 572354.0,
      "end_time": 574604.0,
      "text": "To anyone considering NAND2Tetris,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 574604.0,
      "end_time": 578350.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a tough journey, but you&#39;ll be profoundly changed.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 578350.0,
      "end_time": 583250.0,
      "text": "So Dan demonstrates the many self-learners"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 583250.0,
      "end_time": 587896.0,
      "text": "who take this course off the Web, on their own traction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 587896.0,
      "end_time": 592485.0,
      "text": "on their own initiative, and it&#39;s quite amazing because"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 592485.0,
      "end_time": 597072.0,
      "text": "these people cannot care less about"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 597072.0,
      "end_time": 598314.0,
      "text": "grades."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 598314.0,
      "end_time": 602219.0,
      "text": "They are doing it because of one motivation only."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 602219.0,
      "end_time": 605705.0,
      "text": "They have a tremendous passion to learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 605705.0,
      "end_time": 607629.0,
      "text": "And with that in mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 607629.0,
      "end_time": 612233.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to say a few words about traditional college grading."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 612233.0,
      "end_time": 614593.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sick of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 614593.0,
      "end_time": 616026.0,
      "text": "We are obsessed with grades"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 616026.0,
      "end_time": 617892.0,
      "text": "because we are obsessed with data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 617892.0,
      "end_time": 622479.0,
      "text": "and yet grading takes away all the fun from failing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 622479.0,
      "end_time": 624955.0,
      "text": "and a huge part of education"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 624955.0,
      "end_time": 626546.0,
      "text": "is about failing."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 626546.0,
      "end_time": 629021.0,
      "text": "Courage, according to Churchill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 629021.0,
      "end_time": 631967.0,
      "text": "is the ability to go from one defeat to another"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 631967.0,
      "end_time": 634581.0,
      "text": "without losing enthusiasm. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 634581.0,
      "end_time": 638411.0,
      "text": "And [Joyce] said that mistakes"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 638411.0,
      "end_time": 639880.0,
      "text": "are the portals of discovery."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 639880.0,
      "end_time": 643226.0,
      "text": "And yet we don&#39;t tolerate mistakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 643226.0,
      "end_time": 644535.0,
      "text": "and we worship grades."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 644535.0,
      "end_time": 648323.0,
      "text": "So we collect your B pluses and your A minuses"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 648323.0,
      "end_time": 651160.0,
      "text": "and we aggregate them into a number like 3.4,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 651160.0,
      "end_time": 653071.0,
      "text": "which is stamped on your forehead"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 653071.0,
      "end_time": 655514.0,
      "text": "and sums up who you are."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 655514.0,
      "end_time": 658797.0,
      "text": "Well, in my opinion, we went too far with this nonsense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 658797.0,
      "end_time": 661478.0,
      "text": "and grading became degrading."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 661478.0,
      "end_time": 666379.0,
      "text": "So with that, I&#39;d like to say a few words about upgrading,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 666379.0,
      "end_time": 670804.0,
      "text": "and share with you a glimpse from my current project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 670804.0,
      "end_time": 672834.0,
      "text": "which is different from the previous one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 672834.0,
      "end_time": 674848.0,
      "text": "but it shares exactly the same characteristics"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 674848.0,
      "end_time": 678675.0,
      "text": "of self-learning, learning by doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 678675.0,
      "end_time": 681450.0,
      "text": "self-exploration and community-building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 681450.0,
      "end_time": 687310.0,
      "text": "and this project deals with K-12 math education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 687310.0,
      "end_time": 689214.0,
      "text": "beginning with early age math,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 689214.0,
      "end_time": 693707.0,
      "text": "and we do it on tablets because we believe that"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 693707.0,
      "end_time": 698112.0,
      "text": "math, like anything else, should be taught hands on."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 698112.0,
      "end_time": 701267.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s what we do. Basically, we developed"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 701267.0,
      "end_time": 705025.0,
      "text": "numerous mobile apps, every one of them explaining"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 705025.0,
      "end_time": 706522.0,
      "text": "a particular concept in math."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 706522.0,
      "end_time": 709963.0,
      "text": "So for example, let&#39;s take area."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 709963.0,
      "end_time": 712435.0,
      "text": "When you deal with a concept like area --"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 712435.0,
      "end_time": 717679.0,
      "text": "well, we also provide a set of tools that the child"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 717679.0,
      "end_time": 720310.0,
      "text": "is invited to experiment with in order to learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 720310.0,
      "end_time": 724263.0,
      "text": "So if area is what interests us, then one thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 724263.0,
      "end_time": 728401.0,
      "text": "which is natural to do is to tile the area"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 728401.0,
      "end_time": 732051.0,
      "text": "of this particular shape and simply count"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 732051.0,
      "end_time": 735914.0,
      "text": "how many tiles it takes to cover it completely."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 735914.0,
      "end_time": 738396.0,
      "text": "And this little exercise here gives you a first"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 738396.0,
      "end_time": 741825.0,
      "text": "good insight of the notion of area."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 741825.0,
      "end_time": 744615.0,
      "text": "Moving along, what about the area of this figure?"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 744615.0,
      "end_time": 749272.0,
      "text": "Well, if you try to tile it, it doesn&#39;t work too well, does it."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 749272.0,
      "end_time": 751576.0,
      "text": "So instead, you can experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 751576.0,
      "end_time": 754256.0,
      "text": "with these different tools here by some process"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 754256.0,
      "end_time": 756295.0,
      "text": "of guided trial and error,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 756295.0,
      "end_time": 759133.0,
      "text": "and at some point you will discover that one thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 759133.0,
      "end_time": 762221.0,
      "text": "that you can do among several legitimate transformations"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 762221.0,
      "end_time": 765052.0,
      "text": "is the following one. You can cut the figure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 765052.0,
      "end_time": 768668.0,
      "text": "you can rearrange the parts, you can glue them"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 768668.0,
      "end_time": 771785.0,
      "text": "and then proceed to tile just like we did before."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 771785.0,
      "end_time": 777060.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 777060.0,
      "end_time": 779783.0,
      "text": "Now this particular transformation"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 779783.0,
      "end_time": 783767.0,
      "text": "did not change the area of the original figure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 783767.0,
      "end_time": 785954.0,
      "text": "so a six-year-old who plays with this"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 785954.0,
      "end_time": 788838.0,
      "text": "has just discovered a clever algorithm"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 788838.0,
      "end_time": 792878.0,
      "text": "to compute the area of any given parallelogram."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 792878.0,
      "end_time": 794734.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t replace teachers, by the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 794734.0,
      "end_time": 797863.0,
      "text": "We believe that teachers should be empowered, not replaced."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 797863.0,
      "end_time": 801158.0,
      "text": "Moving along, what about the area of a triangle?"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 801158.0,
      "end_time": 803953.0,
      "text": "So after some guided trial and error,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 803953.0,
      "end_time": 807888.0,
      "text": "the child will discover, with or without help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 807888.0,
      "end_time": 811746.0,
      "text": "that he or she can duplicate the original figure"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 811746.0,
      "end_time": 815154.0,
      "text": "and then take the result, transpose it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 815154.0,
      "end_time": 818902.0,
      "text": "glue it to the original and then proceed [with] what we did before:"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 818902.0,
      "end_time": 826630.0,
      "text": "cut, rearrange, paste — oops— paste and glue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 826630.0,
      "end_time": 828226.0,
      "text": "and tile."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 828226.0,
      "end_time": 832053.0,
      "text": "Now this transformation has doubled the area"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 832053.0,
      "end_time": 835903.0,
      "text": "of the original figure, and therefore we have just learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 835903.0,
      "end_time": 839669.0,
      "text": "that the area of the triangle equals the area of this rectangle"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 839669.0,
      "end_time": 842123.0,
      "text": "divided by two."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 842123.0,
      "end_time": 845571.0,
      "text": "But we discovered it by self-exploration."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 845571.0,
      "end_time": 851651.0,
      "text": "So, in addition to learning some useful geometry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 851651.0,
      "end_time": 856038.0,
      "text": "the child has been exposed to some pretty sophisticated"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 856038.0,
      "end_time": 859065.0,
      "text": "science strategies, like reduction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 859065.0,
      "end_time": 861979.0,
      "text": "which is the art of"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 861979.0,
      "end_time": 865565.0,
      "text": "transforming a complex problem into a simple one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 865565.0,
      "end_time": 867934.0,
      "text": "or generalization, which is at the heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 867934.0,
      "end_time": 870777.0,
      "text": "of any scientific discipline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 870777.0,
      "end_time": 873367.0,
      "text": "or the fact that some properties are invariant"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 873367.0,
      "end_time": 876391.0,
      "text": "under some transformations."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 876391.0,
      "end_time": 879676.0,
      "text": "And all this is something that a very young child"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 879676.0,
      "end_time": 883985.0,
      "text": "can pick up using such mobile apps."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 883985.0,
      "end_time": 887079.0,
      "text": "So presently, we are doing the following:"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 887079.0,
      "end_time": 891388.0,
      "text": "First of all, we are decomposing the K-12 math curriculum"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 891388.0,
      "end_time": 894279.0,
      "text": "into numerous such apps."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 894279.0,
      "end_time": 896856.0,
      "text": "And because we cannot do it on our own,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 896856.0,
      "end_time": 899950.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve developed a very fancy authoring tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 899950.0,
      "end_time": 903225.0,
      "text": "that any author, any parent or actually anyone"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 903225.0,
      "end_time": 905578.0,
      "text": "who has an interest in math education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 905578.0,
      "end_time": 908850.0,
      "text": "can use this authoring tool to develop similar apps"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 908850.0,
      "end_time": 912255.0,
      "text": "on tablets without programming."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 912255.0,
      "end_time": 915475.0,
      "text": "And finally, we are putting together an adaptive ecosystem"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 915475.0,
      "end_time": 918303.0,
      "text": "that will match different learners"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 918303.0,
      "end_time": 923680.0,
      "text": "with different apps according to their evolving learning style."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 923680.0,
      "end_time": 926201.0,
      "text": "The driving force behind this project"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 926201.0,
      "end_time": 929148.0,
      "text": "is my colleague Shmulik London,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 929148.0,
      "end_time": 931792.0,
      "text": "and, you see, just like"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 931792.0,
      "end_time": 935865.0,
      "text": "Salman did about 90 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 935865.0,
      "end_time": 939836.0,
      "text": "the trick is to surround yourself with brilliant people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 939836.0,
      "end_time": 942592.0,
      "text": "because at the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 942592.0,
      "end_time": 944495.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s all about people."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 944495.0,
      "end_time": 947914.0,
      "text": "And a few years ago, I was walking in Tel Aviv"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 947914.0,
      "end_time": 950744.0,
      "text": "and I saw this graffiti on a wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 950744.0,
      "end_time": 952535.0,
      "text": "and I found it so compelling"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 952535.0,
      "end_time": 954678.0,
      "text": "that by now I preach it to my students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 954678.0,
      "end_time": 956944.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d like to try to preach it to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 956944.0,
      "end_time": 958684.0,
      "text": "Now, I don&#39;t know how many people here are familiar"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 958684.0,
      "end_time": 960512.0,
      "text": "with the term &quot;mensch.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 960512.0,
      "end_time": 963120.0,
      "text": "It basically means to be human"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 963120.0,
      "end_time": 965055.0,
      "text": "and to do the right thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 965055.0,
      "end_time": 967484.0,
      "text": "And with that, what this graffiti says is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 967484.0,
      "end_time": 969570.0,
      "text": "&quot;High-tech schmigh-tech."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 969570.0,
      "end_time": 972133.0,
      "text": "The most important thing is to be a mensch.&quot; (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 972133.0,
      "end_time": 975528.0,
      "text": "Thank you. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 975528.0,
      "end_time": 985528.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}